    "text": [
        "Dear Mr Bond,",
        "I'm Serkan who works for retailing department. I want to share my necessary request to you. That's why I write this letter.",
        "In next 5 days I need time off work. Cause of that my child is sick. He is at the hospital with his mother. However, they may need some assistance from me. He is could need my help while he is  resting at he hospital. For example, somebody have to buy some food or water. Additionally, they need clean clothes too. By reason of this I want to some off days of work.",
        "Also, our doctor said that, 5 days is enough for recovery of my child. Therefore, 5 days off work is enough for me.",
        "I want to suggest something for recovering my work. When I start working at company I can fill my duties at the weekends. I would resolve our companies works on this work shift. I wish you could give me some off days work.",
        "Sincerely yours."
    ],
